t is required, write it in English\n    37\t\n    38\t- Repo source comments **m
ust not be in another language** — keep comment language consistent across the r
epo.\n    39\t\n    40\t### §1.3 Examples\n    41\t\n    42\t❌ Non-English revi
ew comment copied straight into source:\n    43\t\n    44\t```python\n    45\tse
lf.logger = logger.bind(channel=self.name)   # ← new\n    46\t```\n    47\t\n   
48\t❌ Neighbors have no comments, yet the new line adds a meaningless one:\n   
