n   298\t**Not allowed:**\n   299\t- pushing and walking away, leaving PR creati
on to the user;\n   300\t- delivering a description without grepping for non-Eng
lish residue.\n   301\t\n   302\t---\n   303\t\n   304\t## 4. Dependencies (uv o
nly)\n   305\t\n   306\t### §4.1 `uv` is the only Python package manager\n   307
\t\n   308\t| Action | Command |\n   309\t|---|---|\n   310\t| Add runtime dep |
