t instructions.\n   329\t\n   330\t---\n   331\t\n   332\t## 5. Tests\n   333\t\
n   334\t### §5.1 Unit tests\n   335\t\n   336\tUnder `tests/test_*.py`. CLI uni
t tests use one shape:\n   337\t\n   338\t```\n   339\ttests/test_cli_<module>_c
ommands.py\n   340\t```\n   341\t\n   342\t- one file per module (aligns with `r
aven/cli/<module>_commands.py`);\n   343\t- **don\'t** split by phase / feature 
/ ticket (no `phase4` / `eve151` suffixes);\n   344\t- aspect suffixes are allow
ed:\n   345\t  - testing a CLI private helper: `test_cli_<helper>.py` (e.g. `tes
t_cli_helpers.py` / `test_cli_stacks.py`);\n   346\t  - cross-module behavior: `
test_cli_<aspect>.py` (e.g. `test_cli_config_precedence.py` / `test_cli_smoke.py
`).\n   347\t\n   348\t### §5.2 Integration tests\n   349\t\n   350\tUnder `test
s/integration/test_*.py`. Run against real environments (real LLM / channel / fc
ntl / subprocess / VM, etc.).\n   351\t\n   352\tNaming: `test_<scope>_<kind>.py
`, where `<kind>` ∈:\n   353\t\n   354\t| kind | Meaning |\n   355\t|---|---|\n 
