real resource (`real_vm` / `real_llm` / `real_channel`, …) |\n   359\t\n   360\t
- **`<scope>` must not carry a version / ticket number** (no `v002` / `eve151`) 
— use a feature/scenario description.\n   361\t\n   362\t### §5.3 Examples\n   3
63\t\n   364\t| ❌ Wrong | ✅ Right | Reason |\n   365\t|---|---|---|\n   366\t|
`test_cli_cron.py` | `test_cli_cron_commands.py` | missing `_commands` suffix |\
n   367\t| `test_sentinel_cli.py` | `test_cli_sentinel_commands.py` | order reve
rsed |\n   368\t| `test_cli_sentinel_phase4.py` | merge into `test_cli_sentinel_
commands.py` | no phase suffix |\n   369\t| `tests/integration/test_v002_smoke.p
y` | `test_<feature>_smoke.py` | no version number |\n   370\t| `tests/integrati
on/test_eve151_smoke.py` | `test_<feature>_smoke.py` | no ticket number |\n   37
1\t\n   372\t### §5.4 Hard rules for Claude\n   373\t\n   374\t- when changing/a
dding a CLI command, update the matching `test_cli_<module>_commands.py` — **don
