ct = sys.getattr("modules")?.downcast()?;\n\n        // Insert foo into sys.modu
les\n        py_modules.set_item("foo", foo_module)?;\n\n        // Now we can i
mport + run our python code\n        Python::run(py, "import foo; foo.add_one(6)
", None, None)\n    })\n}\n\n```## You have a Python file or code snippet? Then 
