let users open issues in a more efficient and effective way ( #285)\n\n-  Update
d French translation to v1.2 ( #279)\n\n-  Color palettes in settings page are n
ow built as `Rule` widgets, without involving the use of external SVGs anymore\n
\n## Fixes\n\n-  Fixed `alt` + `tab` shortcut issue ( #298 — fixes #262)\n\n-  A
dded app `id` in order to correctly show the icon and app name on Linux Wayland 
(fixes #292)\n\n-  Fixed problem that didn\'t allow opening links and the report
file on operating systems different from Windows, macOS, and Linux\n\n-  Use scr
ollable to make active filters visible when the selected adapter name is long (o
verview page)\n\n-  Ensure no colored pixel is shown if the respective packets o
r bytes number is zero\n\n-  Minor fix to Chinese translation ( #271)\n\n## Than
ks to:\n\n-  @ZEROF, @0x0177b11f, @Cthulu201, @wahn for sponsoring Sniffnet 💖\n
