        text='## Summary\n\nI explored `/projects/witt` and the ZeroClaw crates 
it depends on. The user-supplied path `/library/repos/zeroclaw-labs_zeroclaw/cod
e/crates/*` does **not exist** on this filesystem, so I fetched the upstream sou
rce into `/workspace/zeroclaw-src` (`https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw`,
shallow clone, current `main`). All ZeroClaw citations below refer to that check
out.\n\n---\n\n## 1. `/projects/witt` — Witt CLI\n\n### Project metadata\n| Item
| Value | Source |\n|---|---|---|\n| Crate name | `witt` | `/projects/witt/Cargo
.toml:2` |\n| Version | `0.1.0` | `/projects/witt/Cargo.toml:3` |\n| Edition | `
2021` | `/projects/witt/Cargo.toml:4` |\n| Clap | `4` with `derive` | `/projects
/witt/Cargo.toml:8` |\n| Other key deps | `anyhow 1`, `serde 1`, `toml 0.8`, `se
rde_json 1`, `dirs 5`, `async-trait 0.1`, `tokio 1` | `/projects/witt/Cargo.toml
:9-13,28-29` |\n| Lock-file versions | `clap 4.6.1`, `anyhow 1.0.103`, `serde 1.
0.228`, `tokio 1.52.3`, `toml 0.8.23` | `/projects/witt/Cargo.lock` |\n\n### Mod
ule structure\n`main.rs` declares 14 modules:\n\n```rust\nmod agent_zc; mod back
ends; mod classify; mod config; mod daemon;\nmod functions; mod intake; mod inte
nt; mod jobs; mod load; mod memory;\nmod operate; mod router; mod zc;\n```\n\n`/
projects/witt/src/main.rs:1-14`\n\n### Command surface (`clap` derive)\n`Cli` ha
s one subcommand enum `Cmd`:\n\n- `Ask { prompt, backend }`\n- `Route { tag, tas
k }`\n- `Classify { prompt }`\n- `Operate { prompt }`\n- `Agent { Status | Run }
`\n- `Intake { repo }`\n- `Fn { List | Run | Test }`\n- `Watch`\n- `Daemon { Sta
tus | Start | Stop | Enqueue | RunLoop }`\n- `Job { Status | Launch }`\n- `Zc`\n
- `Config`\n\n`/projects/witt/src/main.rs:25-79`\n\n### Key abstractions\n\n####
Config / backends\n- `WittConfig` holds `docker_envs_root`, `default_backend`, a
nd a `BTreeMap<String, Backend>`.\n- `Backend { kind, model, auth, url, notes }`
.\n- Default backends: `hermes` (Hermes Cloud / Ollama Cloud), `qwen-coder` (TBD
), `local` (Ollama local at `127.0.0.1:11434`).\n\n`/projects/witt/src/config.rs
:10-28`, `/projects/witt/src/config.rs:54-95`\n\n#### Router\n- Policy is **data
-driven** from `~/.witt/routing.toml`.\n- `RoutingPolicy { default, routes: BTre
eMap<String, RouteTarget> }`.\n- `RouteTarget` can be a single backend or an ord
ered failover `Chain`.\n- `resolve()` walks the chain, skips unavailable/TBD bac
kends, picks lowest in-flight load.\n\n`/projects/witt/src/router.rs:15-52`, `/p
rojects/witt/src/router.rs:117-163`\n\n#### Memory\n- Phase-4 scaffold: plain ma
rkdown files under `~/.witt/memory/`.\n- `memory_root()`, `ensure_scaffold()`, `
append(topic, line)`.\n\n`/projects/witt/src/memory.rs:10-58`\n\n#### Intent\n- 
`intent::run()` wraps the rules-based `classify::classify()` and then calls the 
`intent-gate` port crate.\n\n`/projects/witt/src/intent.rs:11-20`, `/projects/wi
tt/src/classify.rs:27-69`\n\n#### Operator loop (`operate`)\n- Drives the local 
Ollama `/api/chat` endpoint with a hand-written tool schema (shell, win_ps, list
_dir, read_file, write_file, open_app, which, env_get, memory_*, fn_list, proces
s_list, docker_ps).\n- Has a tiny-model fallback that turns fenced ` ```bash ` b
locks into synthetic tool calls.\n- Uses `repeat_detect::RepeatDetector` for deg
enerate-output detection.\n\n`/projects/witt/src/operate.rs:69-233`, `/projects/
witt/src/operate.rs:237-356`, `/projects/witt/src/operate.rs:413-421`\n\n### Por
t crates wired by Witt\n| Port | Purpose | Key symbol |\n|---|---|---|\n| `inten
t-gate` | Genesis NLU intent detection | `detect_intent()` → `IntentResult` |\n|
`repeat-detect` | Olmocr-style repetition detector | `RepeatDetector::new(8)` / 
`is_degenerate()` |\n\n`/projects/_ports/intent-gate/src/lib.rs:210-287`, `/proj
ects/_ports/repeat-detect/src/lib.rs:7-82`\n\n### Interface to models / “Python 
layer”\nWitt does **not** embed a Python interpreter. It talks to models in thre
e ways:\n\n1. **Hermes cloud lane** — spawns `docker compose run --rm hermes-age
nt chat -q … --model <m> --provider ollama-cloud`.\n2. **Local Ollama** — calls 
`http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/generate` and `/api/chat` via `curl`.\n3. **ZeroClaw
runtime** — `witt agent` uses the full ZeroClaw `Agent` builder.\n\n`/projects/w
itt/src/backends.rs:52-108`, `/projects/witt/src/operate.rs:358-381`\n\n---\n\n#
# 2. ZeroClaw crates (`/workspace/zeroclaw-src`)\n\n### Workspace metadata\n| It
em | Value | Source |\n|---|---|---|\n| Root crate | `zeroclawlabs` | `/workspac
